# AI 1-Person Company Customization (Alpha Forge)

Establish a high-end, autonomous AI 1-person company by integrating assets from `solopreneur-ai-agents` and `chatgpt_prompt_100` into the `alpha-browser` dashboard.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The plan assumes **Luna** is the CEO of this company. I will formalize her persona in the `solopreneur-ai-agents` structure.
> I will also integrate **Kodari (Dev)** and **Youngja (Design)** as core team members in the dashboard.

